quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  4,45,"Ko Alla Teddu…óo Maw…óo On ∆Āuri Anndude ay…ďe mon …ďen onon muumini en, O Humpitii on fii ma…ď…ďe O ∆Āannginni on ngayngu ma…ď…ďe ngun. Alla yonii Gi…óo Reenoowo on, Alla yonii Ballo Da…óndoowo mon pewje ma…ď…ďe e lorra ma…ď…ďe, O Wallay on e ma…ď…ďe."
  4,46,"Hino e …ďeya alyahuudaa…ďe yim…ďe wayliroo…ďe Konngol Alla Jippiingo ngol, …ďe waylira ngol ko ngol jippiniraaka, hi…ďe wi'ana Nulaa…óo on mo jam e kisiyee woni e mun on, tuma on yamiri …ďe fiyaake : "Men nanii haala maa kan, men yeddii yamiroore maa nden", hi…ďe jalkitira wi'ugol : "He…óito ko men wi'aŇčte kon" ; hi…ďe he…ď…ďitora haala ma…ď…ďe "raa'inaa" kan, faandorgol wiide : "He…óito men", si ko woni, ko ittugol yiila …ďe faandorii kon ko …óem…óe ma…ď…ďe wowlata ; ko hu…óugol Nulaa…óo on (yo o his) …ďe faanddii, e yuwugol ka diina. Hara nun …ďe wi'ayno : "Men nanii haala maa kan, men …óoftike yamiroore maa nden", …ďe wi'a: "He…óito", hara …ďe wi'aali : "A nanataa", …ďe wi'a: "He…óito men men gelloo haala maa", …ďe tertoo wi'ugol : "Aynu men" ; ko …óum …ďuraynoo mo∆ī∆īande …ďe, …ďura kadi foccanaade …ďe ; sabu ko …óon woni ne'anagol Nulaa…óo on (yo o his). Ko woni tun, Alla Hu…óii …ďe, O Pottiniri …ďe e Yurmeende Makko nden sabu keeferaaku ma…ď…ďe ngun, …ďe gom…óiŇčtaa gom…óinal nafayngal."
  4,47,"Ko onon yo …ďeya okkanoo…ďe Defte imoorde e Alyahuuda e Annasaare, gom…óinee Nden nde Men Jippini e Muhammadu on mo jam e kisiyee woni e mun, Nden Deftere goonginnde ∆äen won…óe ka mon immorde e Tawreeta e Linjiila, ado Men Mehude momta tere …óen ka geece mon, Men Wa…ótira …óe wano …ďabbe mon …óen, maa Men Wo…ó…óiŇčtina …ďe e Yurmeende Alla nden wano Men Hu…óirnoo yim…ďe asewe …ďen : jaggitunoo…ďe waa√Īugol ngol nden √Īalnde ha…óaande, Alla Wayliri …ďe Bah…ói, Fiyaake Alla on e Kattal Makko ngal Laatike Siinetee…óum."
  4,48,"Pellet, Alla Yawtantaa gooto e tagu Makku ngun kafidugol Mo e go…ó…óum, Himo Yawtana on Mo O Muuyi geddi jaasu…ói sirku, Maa O Leptira …óum nun…óal Makko ngal Mo O Muuyi e ma…ď…ďe yeru bakkaatu ontigi on. Kala non kafidu…óo Alla e go…ó…óum, gom…óii haray o fefindike bakkaatu maw…óo mo yawtantaake."
  4,49,"E a anndaa an Nulaa…óo, fiyaake …ďen la…ď…ďinoo…ďe ko'e mun e golle mun ? Ko woni, ko Alla Tun woni La…ď…ďinoowo on Mo O Muuyi e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen ; tawde ko KaŇčko Anndi ko soomii e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe, …ďe …óuytaŇčtaake huunde e baraaji golle ma…ď…ďe ; hay si fotii wa gaarahun tamaro."
  4,50,"Ndaarii Nulaa…óo, hol no …ďe fefindorta e Alla fenaande tuma …ďe la…ď…ďiŇčta ko'e ma…ď…ďe ! ∆äum …óon yonii bakkaatu fee√Ī√Īi…óo majjere ma…ď…ďe nden."
  4,51,"E hawnaali an Nulaa…óo, fiyaake Alyahuuda …ďen okkanoo…ďe ge…ďal e ganndal, hi…ďe gom…óina …óin rewetee…ói ma…ď…ďe ko woori Alla, …ďe wi'ana yeddu…ďe …ďen : "Ko …ďen …ďuri wonndii…ďe Muhammadu (saw) …ďen feewude laawol ?!"."